{{see|Pullover}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From [[pull]] + [[over]]

===Noun===
'''pullover'''

# A [[sweater]] that must be put on by pulling it over the [[head]]; a sweater without [[button]]s or a [[zipper]] in front
# {{weightlifting}}: An [[exercise]] performed lying on the back in which the arms are [[extend]]ed behind the head and [[exertion]] lifts the [[weight]] above the head.

